<p class="notice--primary"><strong>Watch out!</strong>
The datalogging is build on <a href="https://www.phidgets.com/" target="_blank">Phidgets</a>. Ensure you have the latest Phidgets driver v22 for your platform (e.g. <a href="https://www.phidgets.com/docs/OS_-_Windows" target="_blank">Windows</a>, <a href="https://www.phidgets.com/docs/OS_-_macOS" target="_blank">macOS</a> or <a href="https://www.phidgets.com/docs/OS_-_Linux" target="_blank">Linux</a>) installed.</p>
